msgstr ""
"\t+----------------------------------------+\n"
"\t|\t\t   VIM - main help file  |\n"
"\t|\t\t\t\t\t |\n"
"\t|Desplazarse:  Use las teclas de direcció|\n"
"\t|help.txt================================|\n"
"\t|explorer   |\t\t\t\t |\n"
"\t|dir\t    |~\t\t\t\t |\n"
