#. type: Plain text
#: original/TXT/intro.txt:193
msgid ""
"The Vim editor is based on Stevie and includes (ideas from) other software, "
"worked on by the people mentioned here."
msgstr ""
"El editor Vim está basado en Stevie, e incluye ideas procedentes de otro "
"software, trabajadas por la gente aquí mencionada."

#. type: Plain text
#: original/TXT/intro.txt:193
msgid ""
"Other people helped by sending me patches, suggestions and giving feedback "
"about what is good and bad in Vim."
msgstr ""
"Otra gente me ayudó mediante parches, sugerencias y opiniones acerca de lo "
"bueno y malo de Vim."

#. type: Plain text
#: original/TXT/intro.txt:262
msgid ""
"I wish to thank all the people that sent me bug reports and suggestions."
msgstr ""
"Quisiera dar gracias a toda la gente que envió informes de fallo y "
"sugerencias."

#. type: Plain text
#: original/TXT/intro.txt:262
msgid "The list is too long to mention them all here."
msgstr "La lista es demasiado larga como para mencionarlos a todos aquí."

#. type: Plain text
#: original/TXT/intro.txt:262
msgid ""
"Vim would not be the same without the ideas from all these people: They keep "
"Vim alive!"
msgstr ""
"Vim no sería lo mismo sin las ideas de todas esta gente: ¡Mantienen Vim vivo!"

#. type: Plain text
#: original/TXT/intro.txt:289
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"In this documentation there are several references to other versions of Vi:\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t*Vi* *vi*\n"
"Vi\t\"the original\"."
msgstr ""
"A lo largo de la documentación verá varias referencias a otras versiones de Vi:\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t*Vi* *vi*\n"
"Vi\t«El original»."

#. type: Plain text
#: original/TXT/intro.txt:289
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Without further remarks this is the version\n"
"\tof Vi that appeared in Sun OS 4.x."
msgstr ""
"Sin mas detalle, esta es la versión de Vim que apareció\n"
"\ten Sun Os 4.x."

#. type: Plain text
#: original/TXT/intro.txt:289
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\":version\" returns\n"
"\t\"Version 3.7, 6/7/85\"."
msgstr "«:version» devuelve «Version 3.7, 6/7/85»."

#. type: Plain text
#: original/TXT/intro.txt:289
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Sometimes other versions are referred\n"
"\tto."
msgstr ""
"A veces\n"
"\tencontrara referencias a otras versiones."

#. type: Plain text
#: original/TXT/intro.txt:289
#, no-wrap
msgid "Only runs under Unix."
