"El\n"
"\tcódigo sólo está disponible a través de una licencia."

#. type: Plain text
#: original/TXT/intro.txt:289
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"More information on Vi can be found through:\n"
"\t\thttp://vi-editor.org\t[doesn't currently work...]\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t*Posix*\n"
"Posix\tFrom the IEEE standard 1003.2, Part 2: Shell and utilities."
msgstr ""
"Puede encontrar\n"
"\tmás información a cerca de Vi:\n"
