"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t*Posix*\n"
"Posix\tPertenece al estándar IEEE 1003.2."

#. type: Plain text
#: original/TXT/intro.txt:289
#, no-wrap
msgid "Generally known as \"Posix\"."
msgstr "Parte 2: Consola y utilidades."

#. type: Plain text
#: original/TXT/intro.txt:289
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"This is a textual description of\n"
"\thow Vi is supposed to work."
