#. type: Plain text
#: original/TXT/intro.txt:813
msgid "On the Amiga Vim will run in a CLI window."
msgstr "Vim se ejecutará en una ventana CLI bajo Amiga."

#. type: Plain text
#: original/TXT/intro.txt:813
msgid ""
"The name Vim and the full name of the current file name will be shown in the "
