#. type: Plain text
#: original/txt/usr_41.txt:803
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Syntax and highlighting:\t  *syntax-functions* *highlighting-functions*\n"
"\tclearmatches()\t\tclear all matches defined by |matchadd()| and\n"
"\t\t\t\tthe |:match| commands\n"
