"Vim usará negrita, itálica y texto subrayado, pero esto no es muy\n"
"\tagradable."

#. type: Plain text
#: original/TXT/usr_06.txt:60
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"You probably will want to try to get a terminal with\n"
"\tcolors."
msgstr "Probablemente quiera probar una terminal con colores."

#. type: Plain text
#: original/TXT/usr_06.txt:60
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"For Unix, I recommend the xterm from the XFree86 project:\n"
