"\t|rtunately for the programmer, he |\n"
"\t+---------------------------------+\n"
"After: >"
msgstr ""
"Unfo|\n"
"\t|rtunately for the programmer, he |\n"
"\t+---------------------------------+\n"
"Después: >"

